{"word":"ἄχρι","slug":"ἄχρι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἄχρι, ἄχρις</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>μέχρις</el>; ‘up to a point’ in time or space] a function word signifying an interval between two points with focus on continuity<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of extension in time, ‘onward to or till’, <b><i>until</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b>as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:470 24:38'>Mt 24:38</a>; <a href='B:490 1:20'>Lk 1:20</a>; <a href='B:510 3:21'>Ac 3:21</a>; <a href='B:520 1:13'>Ro 1:13</a>;</b> <el>ἄ. τέλους</el> <i>to the end</i> <b><a href='B:650 6:11'>Hb 6:11</a>;</b> <el>ἄ. ἡμερῶν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πέντε\">πέντε</a></el> <i>within five days</i> <b><a href='B:510 20:6'>Ac 20:6</a>;</b> <el>ἄ. ϑανάτου</el> <i>to the death</i> = until death is exacted (as penalty) <b><a href='B:510 22:4'>22:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ conj.\">conj.</a> with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ rel.\">rel.</a> <el>ἄ. <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὗ\">οὗ</a></el> <i>until</i> (the time when) <b><a href='B:510 7:18'>Ac 7:18</a>; <a href='B:510 27:33'>27:33</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ aor.\">aor.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ subj.\">subj.</a> <b><a href='B:490 21:24'>Lk 21:24</a>; <a href='B:520 11:25'>Ro 11:25</a>.</b> Without <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ rel.\">rel.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὗ\">οὗ</a></el> <b><a href='B:730 7:3'>Rv 7:3</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Rv. <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘up to a certain point’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><i>as far as</i> <a href='B:510 22:22'>Ac 22:22</a>; <a href='B:650 4:12'>Hb 4:12</a>;</b> <el>ἦλϑεν ἄ. ἐμοῦ</el> <i>it came to where I was</i> <b><a href='B:510 11:5'>Ac 11:5</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄχρηστος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄχυρον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}